    shortAnswer: `Revenue operations (RevOps) is the function that aligns marketing, sales, and customer success under shared systems, data, and a single revenue number. It owns the end-to-end funnel, the CRM and tech stack, the data that every metric depends on, and the process and analytics that keep the revenue engine predictable and efficient.`,
